description: Harmony comes to US with bar fighting skills. She is a true brawler and does not hesitate to beat bitches down in a bar that need a good kicking. However, we have structure and rules here. How will a brute strength fighter do against a seasoned US wrestler? Same as most new comers beaten and fucked hard on the mat. The goddess shows she is still a top contender for this seasons title.
title: The Goddess (0-0) vs The Brawler (0-0)
